	[whr].[Interest],
	[whr].[DisplayOrder],
	[whr].[ExtraInfo]
FROM
	[PosInstallment] [whr]
WHERE
	[whr].[BankType] = @bankType_1
ORDER BY
	[whr].[DisplayOrder]
